716#GD|            <article class="testimonial-card">
717#YS|              <div class="quote-mark">"</div>
718#NK|              <p class="testimonial-text">
719#WZ|                The TTC program has been nothing short of a transformational journey. The classes we engaged in,
720#EC|                from Asanas to pranayama to meditation and all the lectures have helped me cultivate greater
721#CQ|                discipline, balance and calm in my day to day life. Physically too, I am a lot more energetic and
722#KW|                stronger. I am amazed at how the principles and philosophy of yoga learnt during the program has
723#LE|                got effortlessly and seamlessly integrated into my daily life making me more self aware, mindful and
724#RE|                productive. It truly was one of the most amazing experiences of my life, layered with learnings,
725#XX|                some of which I am still processing.
726#UF|              </p>
727#NK|              <p class="testimonial-text">
728#BO|                Kudos to the SYGC team whose passion and commitment is just unparalleled. It's Arun and the team
729#KB|                of teachers and their expertise and dedication that make this program stand apart. I would highly
730#HH|                highly recommend this program to anyone looking to deepen their practice and improve the quality
731#MG|                of their life.
732#UF|              </p>
733#FH|              <div class="testimonial-author">— Deepthi</div>
734#SJ|            </article>
