755#NK|              <p class="testimonial-text">
756#VD|                I came over from the US for this course very specifically because of my impression of the excellence
757#FZ|                of the Gurgaon Sivananda teachers based on my online experiences with them. The course proved to
758#XT|                exceed my expectations. Everything was so well designed and created with intentional and positive
759#WU|                purpose. I was fully immersed in the ashram life while I was there and I grew both physically and
760#TU|                intellectually.
761#UF|              </p>
762#NK|              <p class="testimonial-text">
763#AB|                I knew that leaving the ashram and returning home to a different pace may be a challenge, and it
764#VZ|                was, but the simplicity and profundity of the basis of the Sivananda system has provided a solid
765#LB|                foundation which I feel as an accessible grounding point.
766#UF|              </p>
